== functionality ==
up arrow - square moves up until another keypress
down arrow - square moves down until another keypress
left arrow - square moves left until another keypress
right arrow - square moves right until another keypress
x key - square size increases by 2 pixels
z key - square size decreases by 2 pixels
q key - quit game
==========


== overall design ==
3 classes
- Square - represents graphical square
- SquareGame - captures user's inputs, moves square accordingly (in loop)
- Main - starts app, initializes game, launches it

MVC model
- model
- view
- controller
- user
==========
